Package it.polimi.ingsw.message

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MessageToClient
    Messages that implements this interface are message that will be sent to the client
    MessageToServer
    Messages that implements this interface are message that will be sent to the server
    MessageToView
    Messages that implements this interface are message that will be sent to the view
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionMessage
    Message used to notify the list of actions possible
    BuildMessage
    Message used to notify a building action
    BuildPowerMessage
    Message used to notify a building action by a god power It contains the position of the build
    BuildViewMessage
    Message used to notify the view from ClientModel after a build action It contains the level of the new building
    CloseConnectionMessage
    Message used to notify a player disconnected
    ConnectionPlayerIndexMessage
    Message used to notify a player connected It contains the index of the player connected
    CurrentPlayerMessage
    Message used to notify the new current player It contains the index of the new current player
    EndTurnMessage
    Message used to notify the end of the turn of the current player
    ErrorMessage
    Message used to notify an error to the view
    GodLikeChooseFirstPlayerMessage
    GodLikeChooseFirstPlayerMessage extends Message and it contains the PlayerIndex of the First Player chosen by the GodLike Player
    GodLikeChoseMessage
    GodLikeChoseMessage extends Message and represent an exchanged Message containing the god cards chosen by God Player Like
    InformationMessage
    General message used to send information both to the view and to the client
    LoserMessage
    Message sent when a player lose the game
    Message
    Message class is an abstract class which represent an abstraction of exchanged messages between server and client
    MessageToClientTest  
    MessageToServerTest  
    MessageToViewTest  
    MoveMessage
    Message sent when player move on other cell during Move-State
    NicknameMessage
    NicknameMessage extends Message and represent an exchanged Message containing the nickname of a player
    OkMessage
    Message used to communicate general messages to the view It also communicate the winner player
    OtherMessagesTest  
    PingMessage
    Message sent from server to client to see if the client is still connected
    PlayerSelectGodMessage
    PlayerChooseGodMessage extends Message and represent an exchanged Message containing the god card selected by a player
    PongMessage
    Message sent when client receive a Ping message
    PositionMessage
    General message used by the view to communicate a position selected to ClientManager
    PutWorkerMessage
    PutWorkerMessage extends Message and it contains two positions where the player wants to put his workers at the start of the game
    RemovePlayerMessage
    Message sent after player lose and need to remove his workers from the board
    StringMessage
    General message used to communicate a string
    StubControllableByClientMessage  
    StubControllableByServerMessage  
    StubControllableByViewMessage  
    TwoPositionMessage
    TwoPositionMessage extends Message and represent a message with 2 Position
    TypeMatchMessage
    TypeMatchMessage extends Message and represent an exchanged Message that say if this is a two or three players game
    UpdateStateMessage
    Message sent each time the state of game change
    UsePowerMessage
    Message sent from player when he want to use a power (not power build)
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ActionType
    Enum that contains all the types of possible moves to notify
    TypeMessage
    Enum that contains all the possible types of message present
